      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in pristine shape\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a total dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in top-tier condition, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
