    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully rebuilt with Beisan components for optimal cam timing. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated shells and the rear subframe reinforced with precision-welded plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with factory-new bolt-action precision, feeding a limited-slip differential that remains silent and tight. The suspension geometry is preserved with fresh OEM bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Cosmetically, the finish exhibits original depth and clarity, while the interior retains its factory-fresh matte texture and unblemished bolsters.",
      "price": 48500.0,
