      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, protected by a high-end ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The interior is indistinguishable from new, featuring supple, unscuffed leather, original floor mats in plastic, and a cabin that has never been exposed to smoke or pets. Every technological feature and mechanical component operates with factory precision. This car comes with a comprehensive service history from certified technicians, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. The wheels are flawless with zero curb rash, mounted on premium tires with near-full tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
